PECI commands:
 PECI STAT                display return code counts
 PECI STAT CLEAR          reset return code counts
 PECI HIST                display transaction history
 PECI HIST CLEAR          clear transaction history
 PECI SNOOP               view snoop flag
 PECI SNOOP ON            set snoop flag (see PECI transactions as they occur)
 PECI SNOOP OFF           clear snoop flag
 PECI SNOOP DATA          view snoop data flag
 PECI SNOOP DATA ON       set snoop data flag (see data in transactions as they occur)
 PECI SNOOP DATA OFF      clear snoop data flag
 PECI SNOOP ERR           view snoop error flag
 PECI SNOOP ERR ON        set snoop error flag (see errors as transactions fail)
 PECI SNOOP ERR OFF       clear snoop error flag
 PECI SNOOP SMBUS         view snoop smbus flag
 PECI SNOOP SMBUS ON      set snoop smbus flag
 PECI SNOOP SMBUS OFF     clear snoop smbus flag
